text: Ondřej Pažout (born 1 July 1998) is a Czech Nordic combined skier who competes internationally.FIS profile He competed at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Czech Republic Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:People from Turnov Category:Competitors at the 2016 Winter Youth Olympics
